{"name": "vt2geojson", "metadata": {"name": "vt2geojson", "version": "0.2.1", "classifiers": [], "home_page": "https://github.com/Amyantis/python-vt2geojson", "license": "", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["mapbox-vector-tile"], "summary": "Dump vector tiles to GeoJSON from remote URLs or local system files.", "upload_time": 1622463627}, "documentation": ["# python-vt2geojson [![Build Status](https://travis-ci.org/Amyantis/python-vt2geojson.svg?branch=master)](https://travis-ci.org/Amyantis/python-vt2geojson)\nDump vector tiles to GeoJSON from remote URLs or local system files.\n\nInspired from https://github.com/mapbox/vt2geojson.\n\n## Installation\n```\npip install vt2geojson\n```\n\n## Usage\nUsing the CLI:\n```\nvt2geojson --help\n```\n\nMaking a GeoDataframe from a PBF vector tile file:\n```python\nimport geopandas as gpd\nimport requests\n\nfrom vt2geojson.tools import vt_bytes_to_geojson\n\nMAPBOX_ACCESS_TOKEN = \"*****\"\n\nx = 150\ny = 194\nz = 9\n\nurl = f\"https://api.mapbox.com/v4/mapbox.mapbox-streets-v6/{z}/{x}/{y}.vector.pbf?access_token={MAPBOX_ACCESS_TOKEN}\"\nr = requests.get(url)\nassert r.status_code == 200, r.content\nvt_content = r.content\n\nfeatures = vt_bytes_to_geojson(vt_content, x, y, z)\ngdf = gpd.GeoDataFrame.from_features(features)\n```\n\n## Todos:\n* Add more test using `vector-tile/test/fixtures/*.vector.pbf` data files.\n\n## Notes\nThis library has only been tested against **Python 3.6**.\n\nFeel free to [submit your issues](https://github.com/Amyantis/python-vt2geojson/issues).\n\n\n"], "modules": [{"name": "vt2geojson", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "vt2geojson.NAME", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "vt2geojson.DESCRIPTION", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "vt2geojson.AUTHOR", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "vt2geojson.AUTHOR_EMAIL", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "vt2geojson.URL", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "vt2geojson.__version__", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "vt2geojson.tools", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "vt2geojson.tools._is_url", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "uri", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "bool", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bool", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": ["Checks if the uri is actually an url.\n\\:param uri: the string to check.\n\\:return: a boolean.\n"]}, {"name": "vt2geojson.tools.vt_bytes_to_geojson", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "b_content", "type": {"name": "bytes", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bytes", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "x", "type": {"name": "int", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.int", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "y", "type": {"name": "int", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.int", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "z", "type": {"name": "int", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.int", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "layer", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": {"name": "dict", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.dict", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": ["Make a GeoJSON from bytes in the vector tiles format.\n\\:param b_content: the bytes to convert.\n\\:param x: tile x coordinate.\n\\:param y: tile y coordinate.\n\\:param z: tile z coordinate.\n\\:param layer: include only the specified layer.\n\\:return: a features collection (GeoJSON).\n"]}], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "tests.test_conversions", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "tests.test_conversions.DIRPATH", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "tests.test_conversions.SAMPLE_FILEPATH", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "tests.tes